transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Thank you for calling Viagra. How can I help you?

Speaker 2: Yeah, I'm just trying to see if they had shipped my order yet.

Speaker 1: Sure, no problem. Can I just have your name and date of birth?

Speaker 2: Yeah, my name is Westing, M-A-S-U-D, first is S-H-E-R-Y-A-R.

Speaker 1: Thank you, Westing.

Speaker 2: Yeah.

Speaker 1: Okay. All right, it looks like they shipped it out to you today.

Speaker 2: Hold on, where did your profile go?

Speaker 1: All right, they're shipping it out to you today.

Speaker 2: Why was it hold? Oh, okay, I see.

Speaker 1: It was too early for a refill, so the prescription was on hold until yesterday, the 26th.

Speaker 2: So that's why they're shipping it out to you today.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: Okay?

Speaker 1: All right, I should get back in.

Speaker 2: Do you want me to sign up your e-mail for notifications?

Speaker 1: Because I'm on the USGS website.

Speaker 2: What would the notification do?

Speaker 1: Well, it's just the USGS is tracking updates.

Speaker 2: Okay, yeah, that's fine.

Speaker 1: Okay. All right, no problem. I'll add it. You're all set.

Speaker 2: All right, thank you.

Speaker 1: Sure, have a great day.

Speaker 2: You too, bye-bye.

Speaker 1: All right, bye.
